{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act46side", "eventName": "雪山降臨1101", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "OS-3", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "雪灌木中", "storyInfo": "小獵手茱安娜將恩雅帶回家療傷，發現了她的聖女身分，反而開始疏遠她。阿克托斯懷疑刺殺是布朗陶家所為，三族關係再次僵化。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g5_guestroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$saferoom_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$2", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我家。", "name": "小獵手"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$2"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後看到的那些人走了相反的方向，這裡很安全。等處理完你的傷口，你就馬上離開。", "name": "小獵手"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$2"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……謝謝，我——", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "shake", "random": "true", "power": 5.0, "times": 30.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少說話，也別亂動，希瓦艾什。", "name": "小獵手"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$2"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "小獵手"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$2"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "外衣還算厚，距離又遠，傷口不是很深。", "name": "小獵手"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$2"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不過他們用的箭有一個小倒鉤，拔的時候會很痛，我儘量小心處理。", "name": "小獵手"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$2"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年輕的獵手將箭桿折斷一截，她捏緊剩餘的部分，目光瞟向傷者，而對方只是輕輕點頭，沒有流露出一絲恐慌。"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獵手深深呼吸，緩緩地拔出箭鏃，倒鉤牽動肉體的觸感讓她也不禁冷汗直流。"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她竭盡全力地讓雙手穩定，直至箭鏃完全從對方的身上分離。"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#7$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼——呼——總算……", "name": "小獵手"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#7$2"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "非常……感謝……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還沒弄好，你再忍一下。", "name": "小獵手"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$2"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothtrailground", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緊接著她從腰包裡拿出一包藥粉，挽起恩雅的裙襬，熟練地抹勻在她的傷口上，又拿出一根布條將那裡緊緊包紮起來。"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "痛的話可以叫出來，我不會笑你的。", "name": "小獵手"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$2"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不想讓你更加緊張。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬一手抖了，我自己也會更不舒服。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘁。", "name": "小獵手"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$2"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯？", "name": "小獵手"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$2"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一隻雪白的小雲獸從獵手的帽兜中探出細長的身體，雙爪扒著獵手的髮辮，濕潤的鼻頭在恩雅的毛領邊微微顫動。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨後，牠伸著腦袋嗅聞著陌生人的氣味。"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別碰牠，牠很討厭陌生人。", "name": "小獵手"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不等獵手說完，恩雅的手指已經輕輕揉上了小雲獸的下巴。僅僅是撫摸到牠柔軟的皮毛，彷彿內心在嚴寒下也能升起一絲暖意。"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（壓低聲音）裂雲獸，快點回去……", "name": "小獵手"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個小傢伙……叫“裂雲獸”嗎？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我還不知道你的名字呢，我的救星大人。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "小獵手"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#4$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茱安娜。", "name": "小獵手"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並不想知道你叫什麼，希瓦艾什。你最好別以為我是你的朋友。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼？你對我很好啊。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你們又是怎麼對我的！", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼……跟你也沒關係，不說了。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“你們”的意思，是指希瓦艾什家嗎？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者，你在說恩希歐迪斯……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#2$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不只他一個。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我父親說，從恩希歐迪斯的父親開始，希瓦艾什就痴迷於褻瀆耶拉岡德。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他把瀝青澆淋在耶拉岡德的脊骨，把毒水傾倒在耶拉岡德的尾巴，他的貪婪也為自己帶來了毀滅。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結果現在，這個恩希歐迪斯完全沒有吸取教訓，他變本加厲地攪擾耶拉岡德的安寧。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他最重的罪孽，是他竟敢在耶拉岡德的血肉上開了一個大洞。這次的災禍，不就是希瓦艾什惹怒了耶拉岡德的證明？", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是……謝拉格人不可能永遠困在雪山。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "工業和商業不是真的讓我們過上更好的生活了嗎？慈悲的耶拉岡德怎麼會因為我們過上了好日子而懲罰我們呢？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更好的生活？", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們希瓦艾什能有這副鬼樣，天天躲在溫暖的壁爐邊吃香喝辣……", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "茱安娜", "content": "靠的……"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "茱安娜", "content": "就是把我們變成代價！"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我小時候，雪山腳下還棲息著許多獸群。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牠們以山川為給養，到溪流邊飲用清水，回山林裡啃食草木與漿果，如此度過千年，從未改變。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是喀蘭貿易卻把鐵軌一路修到這裡，硬生生把山川分割開來，逼著野獸冒死來回跨過鐵軌才能生存。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "偶爾有列車撞死了牠們，你們竟還抱怨是牠們不長眼睛。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獸群們只能往更高的地方遷居，但山上的土地根本不夠養活數量那麼龐大的族群，牠們互相爭鬥、撕咬，能活下來的越來越少。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更別說還有許多對列車噪音敏感的雲獸……這其中有多少生靈逝去，我又是怎麼收養到了裂雲獸，你根本就不懂！", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……可是，山腳下的農民們，需要那些列車送來的肥料與種子；山上的病人，也需要那些藥物。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那耶拉岡德賜予我們的富足獵獲又在哪裡呢？", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每年我們打到的獵物，都比過去一年更少，連泉水也不再像以往那麼清甜。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們家族遵循著耶拉岡德神聖的教誨，世世代代在山上以狩獵謀生，為此還會雕刻聖像以表敬愛。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "父親……還有我，甚至弟弟妹妹，也向來虔心祈禱，不敢對耶拉岡德輕慢一次。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "憑什麼成為“代價”的是我們？！", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突然的叫聲讓裂雲獸有些驚怕，牠從渾身發抖的茱安娜身上躍下，徘徊在恩雅的腳邊。"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅俯身抱起裂雲獸，將牠送回茱安娜的肩上。"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……別再這麼亂動了，傷口容易裂開。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實……你說的這些，我都是第一次聽到。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你想反駁什麼，儘管說吧，希瓦艾什。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我不想反駁。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……有些不同，很多時候必須要待在房子裡，只能從別人的口中瞭解現在的謝拉格。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使有些日子，我能走出常住的地方，親身體會謝拉格的一切，也遠遠不夠。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德不會放棄每一個謝拉格子民，我向你保證。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#3$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼……", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還是先保證自己能平安度過眼前的危難吧……", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話又說回來，那些土匪是怎麼回事？山上的幾家獵戶我基本都認識，剛才的人裡並沒有熟面孔。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#9$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們……或許是為我而來的。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#4$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為你？你有什麼仇人嗎？", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#9$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……唔，說來話長了。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#4$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果是這樣，你今天最好就別走了，他們肯定不會放棄。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我父親的朋友在城裡開雜貨店，弟弟妹妹這幾天也在他那裡幫忙，我現在就下山去找他多拿點藥膏和箭頭。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還能叫一些熟人上來一起對付那群土匪。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "絕對不行。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一個人很害怕嗎？我腳程很快，精力也很好，現在下山的話明早就能回來。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是擔心這個……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼？你們希瓦艾什真是麻煩，支支吾吾半天都說不清楚。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要是不能戰鬥，說什麼我都得去城裡找幫手，就這麼定了。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.7, "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，我可以告訴你——", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#6$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_chairbump", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅急切地起身，伸手拉住了正準備離開的獵手的袖角，自己身著的斗篷也隨激烈的動作落下。"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……！", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女……大人……？", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#5$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實……我……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起！！", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛剛頂撞了聖女大人！請您懲罰我吧！", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……我怎麼會懲罰你……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你先別著急，先坐下……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_runstop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅想要拉住茱安娜，對方卻迅速後退一步，拉開和恩雅的距離。"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她轉身要走，突然又彷彿想起了什麼，轉過身對著恩雅恭恭敬敬地行了一禮，這才離開了房間。"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_vipward", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loading_intro", "key": "$loading_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "古羅將軍……", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#4$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_260_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，原來是馬特洪家的小子，*謝拉格俚語*，進來之前都不敲個門。", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#7$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼來了？", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#7$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我陪恩希亞小姐來做檢查，她早上也遇上了車禍，幸好沒受什麼傷。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結果聽說你也在這裡，順便來探望——你還好嗎？", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_260_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "古羅", "content": "哼，我身上這點小傷隨便撐一下就過去了，但是——"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_260_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "古羅", "content": "等等，你說你們家二小姐怎麼樣了？"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很不巧，恩希亞小姐她早上替老爺送東西，去蔓珠院的山路上撞上了對向車道的車，要不是鐧小姐及時抵達，差一點就釀成大禍了。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_260_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是說她也要去蔓珠院？", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#7$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怪了，我家老爺也是今早突然收到了蔓珠院的通知，說是要早上提前去開會，結果就在山路上碰到了落石。", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#7$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那你有聽說，布朗陶家出了什麼事嗎？", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#7$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……暫時還沒有聽說。布朗陶家怎麼了嗎？", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_260_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怪不得……怪不得剛才老爺走的時候氣勢洶洶的，好久沒見他發這麼大火。", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_260_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是這搞的——唉！", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#5$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_260_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "馬特洪兄弟，請你一定要幫這忙。能不能麻煩請你家老爺，現在就帶人去布朗陶家？", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我家大人比我還衝動，就怕這個時候會做傻事，或許只有恩希歐迪斯老爺能攔住他了。", "name": "古羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_260_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好……我這就安排。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g8_nobleroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……阿克托斯，在你進一步發瘋前，我真誠地建議你先到醫院做個全面的檢查，輕度腦震盪的症狀並不明顯，最容易被人忽略。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要轉移話題！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正面回答我，為什麼只有我和希瓦艾什遭受到了襲擊，而你們幾個布朗陶卻安心地躲在家裡，你到底知道些什麼？！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我對今天發生的事瞭解的所有資訊，全部都來源於你。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還想狡辯？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聯絡希瓦艾什家的時候，那邊的傭人都知道要關心我幾句，還告訴我恩希亞也被騙走的消息。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你呢？從始至終都是這一副若無其事的樣子！好像這種事發生了也沒什麼稀奇的，這就是布朗陶家的態度？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我為我的態度向你致歉。這幾天所有謝拉格人都過得很艱難，希望能得到你的諒解。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收起這副惺惺作態的樣子，我受夠了。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家都說，如今的布朗陶家出了個妖婦。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前我從沒把這句話當回事，只要你的所作所為是為了謝拉格和耶拉岡德，無論做什麼我都不在乎。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但現在呢？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菈塔托絲，耶拉岡德什麼時候教你這套暗算盟友的陰險手段了？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "注意你的措辭，阿克托斯。即使你試圖諷刺和激怒我，言語裡也不能對耶拉岡德不敬。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要避開重點！現在是我在問你，直接回答我的問題！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和恩希亞被人襲擊的事，布朗陶家到底有沒有參與？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在浪費時間，我重複了很多次：我對此毫不知情，並深表遺憾。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果這就是你的最終答覆，那就別怪我把事情做得太絕。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼意思？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別以為你們弄傷了古羅，佩爾羅契家就無人可用了。我出門前就已經安排了手下，讓他們準時來到這裡“接應”。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "布朗陶家必須被徹底搜查。儘管我也不想走到這一步，但現在看來，不得不委屈一下休露絲和她的孩子了。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你敢？！", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#8$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是你逼我的，菈塔托絲！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_dooropen", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_swordexsheath", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_attack_ready", "volume": 0.8, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "客廳的大門毫無徵兆地被打開了。在開門聲傳來的剎那，阿克托斯毫不猶豫地拔出佩刀。"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼尖的布朗陶家護衛們也旋即舉起武器，擋在菈塔托絲的身前。"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想必，大家已經討論過今天發生的事件了。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我同樣為這件事而來，並且已有一些結論，還請二位不用如此緊張。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_unsheathe", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看到阿克托斯先收起了佩刀，菈塔托絲對著護衛們輕輕揮手，眾人才緩緩退開。"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你來的正好，恩希歐迪斯。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我代表佩爾羅契，你代表希瓦艾什，一同要求徹查布朗陶家的全部文件，相關布朗陶家族成員也得配合我們的詢問。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，阿克托斯，我並不這麼想。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倘若菈塔托絲希望除掉你我，那麼她的動機是什麼？", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這個節骨眼，用暗殺的方式處理另外兩家的家主，只會引起更大的騷亂。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "佩爾羅契家擁有最龐大的士兵隊伍，希瓦艾什家維持著喀蘭貿易的運轉。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使你我同時意外身故，菈塔托絲不僅不可能控制謝拉格的局面，反而會面臨猛烈的報復。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說得對嗎？", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菈塔托絲避開恩希歐迪斯的注視，只是微微頷首。"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那這也不能解釋，為什麼只有布朗陶家沒有被襲擊。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許只是巧合或者時機不對，襲擊者是否安排了針對布朗陶家的行動我們也不得而知。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "光是“巧合”是無法說服我的，恩希歐迪斯。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果不是菈塔托絲，那究竟是什麼人會做出這種事情？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這件事的真相不是短時間內就可以得出的。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別忘了，如今謝拉格泥沙俱下，想要趁亂分一杯羹的絕不在少數。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在維多利亞送來援助的時間點上，行刺殺之舉，顯然對方覺得不能讓我們繼續這麼合作下去。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是維多利亞人幹的？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不只他們，在此刻介入謝拉格事宜的外國政客都脫不了嫌疑。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我希望能維持上一次會議最後的結論——由我來負責包括維多利亞在內的所有對外事務。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一定會查明真相，為了佩爾羅契，為了三族的和平……也為了恩希亞。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我最後一次相信你……", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼……", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要得意，菈塔托絲。看在恩希歐迪斯和休露絲的份上，今天算你走運！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是發現確實是你在背後搞鬼，我絕不饒你！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_smashtable", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這位健壯的烏薩斯一拍桌子，猛地轉身離去。"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……恩希歐迪斯，你能為我平息那個瘋子的怒火，我很感激。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過我已經很累了，相信你也明白，應對無端的指責有多麼令人疲憊。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你對我有所懷疑，希望從我這裡問出些什麼，我——", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必多說，我理解。如今三族之間的信任比什麼都重要。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還有要緊的事務需要處理，就不繼續打擾了。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不送。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G4_kjeragstreet", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以放心了，恩希亞沒事。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們原本是針對我來的。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很顯然。我檢查過現場，很有可能是人為製造的車禍。他們應該是盯上了你的車子，但是不知道車裡坐的是誰。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不對勁……做法太誇張了，但背後的人簡直就像在明說，他們根本不避諱採用這種激烈手段。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#7$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……他們的主要目的是引發混亂與猜忌，行為比結果更加重要。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#5$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另一方面，如果說還有什麼可能……我或者恩希亞以及阿克托斯，都不是他們的真正目標。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#5$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……雪山上有麻煩了。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#5$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……他們的目標是恩雅？", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#4$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果這個時候聖女出了什麼意外，更是坐實了那些陰謀論謠言，謝拉格將會深陷泥沼。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鐧，我需要你保護恩雅。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅已經出發很久了，我不能向你許下任何承諾。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要做最壞的打算，恩希歐迪斯。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信恩雅。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你用了“相信”這個詞。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不像往常那樣，多分析一點理由，好讓我更有信心嗎？", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}